commitResults.messageBody:
Changes :
- MainWindow now complies more with being a main window abstraction, instead of being the base class from which other page types extend.
- Add contentPlaceholder StackPane to display the Page node
- Add switchHandler to mainWindow to handle page transitions and set commandUpdater callback
- Add Page abstract class UiPart, from which all pages will extend
